  <project_license>GPL-3.0-or-later</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      QSpeakers is a simple graphical program that simulates common acoustical enclosures behaviour to help designing loudspeaker systems, based on the loudspeaker driver&apos;s Thiele / Small parameters and the chosen enclosure type.
    </p>
    <p>
      This software is mostly useful for do-it-yourself loudspeaker enthusiasts, acoustics teaching, and to a lesser extent, for loudspeaker engineering.
    </p>
  </description>
  
